{"title":"The Wolf’s Postcript to ‘Little Red Riding Hood’","author":{"name":"Agha Shahid Ali"},"publishDate":"2011-08-04","lines":[{"line":"First, grant me my sense of history:","stanza":1,"number":1},{"line":"I did it for posterity,","stanza":1,"number":2},{"line":"for kindergarten teachers","stanza":1,"number":3},{"line":"and a clear moral:","stanza":1,"number":4},{"line":"Little girls shouldn’t wander off","stanza":1,"number":5},{"line":"in search of strange flowers,","stanza":1,"number":6},{"line":"and they mustn’t speak to strangers.","stanza":1,"number":7},{"line":"And then grant me my generous sense of plot:","stanza":2,"number":8},{"line":"Couldn’t I have gobbled her up","stanza":2,"number":9},{"line":"right there in the jungle?","stanza":2,"number":10},{"line":"Why did I ask her where her grandma lived?","stanza":2,"number":11},{"line":"As if I, a forest-dweller,","stanza":2,"number":12},{"line":"didn’t know of the cottage","stanza":2,"number":13},{"line":"under the three oak trees","stanza":2,"number":14},{"line":"and the old woman lived there","stanza":2,"number":15},{"line":"all alone?","stanza":2,"number":16},{"line":"As if I couldn’t have swallowed her years before?","stanza":2,"number":17},{"line":"And you may call me the Big Bad Wolf,","stanza":3,"number":18},{"line":"now my only reputation.","stanza":3,"number":19},{"line":"But I was no child-molester","stanza":3,"number":20},{"line":"though you’ll agree she was pretty.","stanza":3,"number":21},{"line":"And the huntsman:","stanza":4,"number":22},{"line":"Was I sleeping while he snipped","stanza":4,"number":23},{"line":"my thick black fur","stanza":4,"number":24},{"line":"and filled me with garbage and stones?","stanza":4,"number":25},{"line":"I ran with that weight and fell down,","stanza":4,"number":26},{"line":"simply so children could laugh","stanza":4,"number":27},{"line":"at the noise of the stones","stanza":4,"number":28},{"line":"cutting through my belly,","stanza":4,"number":29},{"line":"at the garbage spilling out","stanza":4,"number":30},{"line":"with a perfect sense of timing,","stanza":4,"number":31},{"line":"just when the tale","stanza":4,"number":32},{"line":"should have come to an end.","stanza":4,"number":33}]}